SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[AppUserId], [t].[CreateDate], [b0].[Id], [b0].[BasketId], [b0].[Count], [b0].[CreateDate], [b0].[ProductId]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [b].[Id], [b].[AppUserId], [b].[CreateDate]
    FROM [Baskets] AS [b]
    WHERE 0 = 1
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN [BasketProducts] AS [b0] ON [t].[Id] = [b0].[BasketId]

    SELECT TOP(1) [b].[Id], [b].[AppUserId], [b].[CreateDate]
    FROM [Baskets] AS [b]

SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[AppUserId], [t].[CreateDate], [b0].[Id], [b0].[BasketId], [b0].[Count], [b0].[CreateDate], [b0].[ProductId]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [b].[Id], [b].[AppUserId], [b].[CreateDate]
    FROM [Baskets] AS [b]
    WHERE 0 = 1
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN [BasketProducts] AS [b0] ON [t].[Id] = [b0].[BasketId]
